                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-287-off1524 t18311201-287-crimeloc1527"></join> - the prisoner is my cousin. On the 26th of November he came and drank tea with me and my wife; we went to wind some quills at the other end of the shop - the prisoner was then leaning against my loom-post; he then went down stairs, and I went to my loom and missed a trevet, with which we cut the plush; I afterwards saw him in custody,</p>
               <p>
            
